column5: THE BADGER WILL HEAD UP TO SCOUT LAKE CAMP NEXT WEEK AND IS LOOKING FOR SOME INFO ON THE FISHING IN THAT AREA OF LAC SEUL.
THE BADGER WILL HEAD UP TO SCOUT LAKE CAMP NEXT WEEK AND IS LOOKING FOR SOME INFO ON THE FISHING IN THAT AREA OF LAC SEUL.

Check out http://www.justfishontario.com/reports.htm, they have two reports from Lac Seul on there. Both are not far from Scout Lake, especially Evergreen Lodge. Fishing has been excellent on Lac Seul although it has slowed a little last week.
